title: Starenky
text:
Starenky () is a <a href="types%20of%20inhabited%20localities%20in%20Russia">rural locality</a> (a <a href="Village%23Russia">khutor</a>) in Kirovskoye Rural Settlement, <a href="Sredneakhtubinsky%20District">Sredneakhtubinsky District</a>, <a href="Volgograd%20Oblast">Volgograd Oblast</a>, Russia. The population was 243 as of 2010.
Geography.
Starenky is located 24 km northwest of <a href="Srednyaya%20Akhtuba">Srednyaya Akhtuba</a> (the district's administrative centre) by road. Prikanalny is the nearest rural locality.
